						<xsd:annotation>
							<xsd:documentation source="http://www.openapplications.org/oagis/10">Is where the information that the BOD message carries is provided, in this case GetCredit. The information consists of a Verb and one or more Nouns. The verb (Get) indicates the action to be performed on the Noun (Credit).</xsd:documentation>
